# 🐍 Snake Game (Java Swing)

## 📌 Project Description
A GUI-based Snake Game developed using Java Swing.
The game includes keyboard controls, food generation, collision detection, and game over logic.

## 🚀 Features
- Snake movement using arrow keys
- Random food generation
- Collision detection (wall & self)
- Game over screen
- Timer-based game loop

## 🛠 Technologies Used
- Core Java
- Java Swing
- OOP Concepts
- Event Handling
